<div class="activities">
  <h2>ACTIVITIES</h2>
  <p>
    If you are looking for an active holiday, Svendborg is the perfect starting point. Svendborg's breathtaking coastline invites adventure seekers to explore its waters through kayaking, paddleboarding, and sailing, offering a thrilling blend of
    sport and natural beauty. </p>
    <img src="../images/active.jpg" alt="" />
    <p>Hiking and biking trails weave through Svendborg's lush forests and picturesque landscapes, providing opportunities for outdoor enthusiasts to immerse themselves in nature.Svendborg's favorable wind conditions make it a haven for wind and
    kite surfers, who can take advantage of the open waters and exhilarating waves.
    </p>
  
</div>


<div class="nature">
  <h2>NATURE</h2>
  <p>
    With its diverse natural offerings, Svendborg captivates visitors with its coastal beauty, verdant forests, picturesque islands, and serene parks, making it an ideal destination for those seeking a connection with nature. Nestled on the coast,
    Svendborg offers breathtaking views of the sea, with tranquil beaches perfect for sunbathing, picnicking, and leisurely walks along the shoreline. <br />
    <br />The town is surrounded by lush forests and rolling hills, providing numerous hiking and biking trails that showcase the area's natural beauty, allowing visitors to explore at their own pace.
  </p>
